videos.headline: Nye says Alabama's offensive patience was key vs. Vandy
videos.description: After scoring 23 with five triples in a late 74-66 comeback over the Commodores, Aaliyah Nye shouts out Sarah Ashlee Barker and details the Tide's second-half spark.
